    func printLog(message: NSString){
        #if VERBOSE_LOG
            #if os(OSX)
                let OS="OS X"
            #else
                let OS="iOS"
            #endif

            #if arch(arm) || arch(arm64)
                let devicetype = "Mobile device"
            #elseif arch(x86_64) || arch(i386)
                let devicetype = "Computer"
            #else
                let devicetype = "Unkown"
            #endif

            NSLog("%@ on a %@ - %@", OS, devicetype, message)
        #endif
    }
